<br>
Once your passed the graveyard area, you can most times invis yourselfs in to the prince prep corner... all pop invis and take out the couple mobs there, med/buff and start pulling to there... or scout out a closer place to invis to and repeat...<br>
<br>
High levels on the raids will help alot, having a few low levels causes aggro to spread further when fighting, so you will likely get an extra add or 3 late... if your skilled and prepared, that shouldnt be a problem, but it could take you by surprise and/or be too much on a close fight...<br>
